@startuml Admin_Authentication

title Admin - Authentication (Module A)

actor Admin as "🔐 Admin"

rectangle "AUTHENTICATION & VERIFICATION" {
    usecase "Verify Candidate\nSignup" as A1
    usecase "Verify Recruiter\nSignup" as A2
    usecase "Admin Login" as A3
    usecase "Admin Logout" as A4
    usecase "Verify Email\nConfirmation" as A8
}

Admin --> A3: 1. Login
Admin --> A1: 2. Verify candidate signup
A1 --> A8: Confirm email
Admin --> A2: 3. Verify recruiter signup
A2 --> A8: Confirm email
Admin --> A4: 4. Logout

note right of A3
  **Priority:** P0 (Critical)
  **Status:** Implemented ✅
end note

@enduml
